    dc:description "FIGURES 3–10. Cavonus sculpturatus Blackburn, 1888, holotype male. 3, Dorsum; 4, venter; 5, lateral; 6, head, lateral; 7, head, dorsal; 8, pygidium; 9, parameres, apices missing; 10, aedeagus, lateral." ;
